OL,3,C'We lost the meaning of life': ITV
OL,4,CNews video journalist in Gaza reflects
OL,5,Con war
OL,7,FAfter 732 days of war, Mohammed Abu
OL,8,FSafia says Palestinians have been
OL,9,F"given another chance"
OL,11,FA Palestinian video journalist who has
OL,12,Fbeen covering the conflict in Gaza for
OL,13,FITV News has spoken of his sadness at
OL,14,Fthe loss of life, but his relief that
OL,15,Fthose who survived have been given
OL,16,Fanother chance.
OL,18,F"I don't know if I feel happy or sad,"
OL,19,FMohammed Abu Safia said following the
OL,20,Fnews that a peace deal had been agreed
OL,21,Fbetween Israel and Hamas.
