OL,3,C'We lost the meaning of life': ITV
OL,4,CNews video journalist in Gaza reflects
OL,5,Con war
OL,7,FMohammed has been covering the
OL,8,Fconflict in Gaza for ITV News since
OL,9,FOctober 7, where outside news crews
OL,10,Fhave been - and remain - banned by
OL,11,FIsrael.
OL,13,F"In this war, we lost people we loved
OL,14,Fand people who loved life. We lost
OL,15,Fcivilians, friends, and family
OL,16,Fmembers," he said.
OL,18,F"We lost many of our memories. We lost
OL,19,Fthe meaning of life itself. But today,
OL,20,Fwe've been given another chance."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
