OL,3,C'We lost the meaning of life': ITV
OL,4,CNews video journalist in Gaza reflects
OL,5,Con war
OL,7,FIsrael and Hamas have both agreed to
OL,8,Fthe first phase of a peace deal to end
OL,9,Fthe war in Gaza. But an organised
OL,10,Fpeace won't undo the loss, and any
OL,11,Fhappiness is clouded by trauma,
OL,12,FMohammed says.
OL,14,F"Today, we've been given another
OL,15,Fchance to start a new life after all
OL,16,Fwe've been through during this war.
OL,17,FAll kinds of killing, all kinds of
OL,18,Fsuffering, things a human being can
OL,19,Fimagine, or can't even imagine, to be
OL,20,Fhonest," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
