OL,3,C'We lost the meaning of life': ITV
OL,4,CNews video journalist in Gaza reflects
OL,5,Con war
OL,7,F"Where I'm standing now is a hospital
OL,8,Fwhere I've been taking shelter, a
OL,9,Fplace full of memories from the past
OL,10,Ftwo years.
OL,12,F"We lost people we lived with and
OL,13,Fshared good times with. Others were
OL,14,Finjured. What's even harder than
OL,15,Flosing loved ones, memories, and
OL,16,Fhomes," he told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
