OL,3,C'We lost the meaning of life': ITV
OL,4,CNews video journalist in Gaza reflects
OL,5,Con war
OL,7,FDescribing October 7 as a living hell
OL,8,Ffor the residents of Gaza, for the
OL,9,Ffirst time, he experienced an internal
OL,10,Fconflict between working to cover the
OL,11,Fwar and protecting his family, looking
OL,12,Ffor a safe place for them.
OL,14,FFive months later, he managed to
OL,15,Fevacuate his then-pregnant wife and
OL,16,Fthree children to Egypt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
