OL,3,C'We lost the meaning of life': ITV
OL,4,CNews video journalist in Gaza reflects
OL,5,Con war
OL,7,F"I've been away from my family for
OL,8,Falmost two years now. They're in Egypt
OL,9,Fto make sure they're safe, so I can
OL,10,Fkeep doing my work, keep running,
OL,11,Fchasing stories, and sometimes
OL,12,Fsleeping rough. I miss holding my
OL,13,Fnewborn son," he said.
OL,15,F"I can't reunite with them because the
OL,16,Fcrossing is closed. The war has
OL,17,Fstopped, but the crossing is still
OL,18,Fshut."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
