OL,3,C'We lost the meaning of life': ITV
OL,4,CNews video journalist in Gaza reflects
OL,5,Con war
OL,7,FSarja Hammand had to be dug out of
OL,8,Frubble by hand after her home was hit
OL,9,Fby an Israeli airstrike, something
OL,10,FMohammed captured on camera
OL,12,FThe blast was so devastating that many
OL,13,Fbodies were never recovered. The
OL,14,Fthought of what could have happened if
OL,15,Fhe had stayed continues to haunt him.
OL,17,FDespite the months that have passed,
OL,18,FMohammed has yet to find a truly safe
OL,19,Fplace. "There is no such thing as
OL,20,Fsafety here," he said.
