OL,3,C'We lost the meaning of life': ITV
OL,4,CNews video journalist in Gaza reflects
OL,5,Con war
OL,7,FAmong the countless stories he has
OL,8,Fcovered, one lingers: an interview
OL,9,Fwith Mohammed Abu Sahloul, conducted
OL,10,Fjust minutes before he was shot and
OL,11,Fkilled by Israeli forces
OL,13,FIt took three days to locate the man's
OL,14,Ffamily, displaced like so many others.
OL,15,FThe killing, Mohammed says, was a war
OL,16,Fcrime.
OL,18,F"I can't really feel happy after all
OL,19,Fthe sadness we've lived through these
OL,20,Fpast two years," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
