OL,3,C'We lost the meaning of life': ITV
OL,4,CNews video journalist in Gaza reflects
OL,5,Con war
OL,7,F"I hope we'll have a better future...
OL,8,Fand that we'll have the chance to see
OL,9,Fthe world and for the world to see us."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
